ate soldier  The Governor proposed and the Board of Visitors approved the establishment of two  Jackson Hope Medals  to be presented annually to the two most distinguished graduates of the Institute  and since the first awards in 1877  the Jackson Hope Medals have been VMI s highest awards for scholastic achievement All Majors All Majors Jackson Hope Medals In 1867 the Honorable A  J  B  Beresford Hope  member of the British Parliament and representative of an association that had presented to the Commonwealth of Virginia a statue of Thomas J  Jackson  sent to Governor James L  Kemper the remainder of the statue fund  requesting that it be used for a further memorial to the great Confederate soldier  The Governor proposed and the Board of Visitors approved the establishment of two  Jackson Hope Medals  to be presented annually to the two most distinguished graduates of the Institute  and since the first awards in 1877  the Jackson Hope Medals have been VMI s highest awards for scholastic achievement Jackson Hope Medals Jackson Hope Medals In 1867 the Honorable A  J  B  Beresford Hope  member of the British Parliament and representative of an association that had presented to the Commonwealth of Virginia a statue of Thomas J  Jackson  sent to Governor James L  Kemper the remainder of the statue fund  requesting that it be used for a further memorial to the great Confederate soldier  The Governor proposed and the Board of Visitors approved the establishment of two  Jackson Hope Medals  to be presented annually to the two most distinguished graduates of the Institute  and since the first awards in 1877  the Jackson Hope Medals have been VMI s highest awards for scholastic achievement  All Majors Jeff Shaara  Scholar in Residence Award  Established in 1999  Annual award to provide the opportunity to pursue a research topic relating to mid nineteenth century American history and to serve as a historical interpreter at  New Market  Battlefield  State Historical  Park  The